 Zettl räumliche Einschlüsse im Film auf ihre narrativen, ästhetischen und epistemologischen Dimensionen und legt damit die erste Studie zu diesem omnipräsenten, aber bislang übersehenen Motiv vor.  afunded by Swiss National Science Foundation (SNSF)  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mrz 2022) 4aAlfred Hitchcock. 4aBox. 4aDavid Lynch. 4aEpistemologie. 4aFilmgeschichte. 4aGeorges Méliès. 4aInszenierung. 4aKino. 4aKiste. 4aMedienwissenschaft. 4aMotiv. 4aNarratologie. 4aRaum. 4aSchachtel. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Media Studies.2bisacsh  aAlfred Hitchcock.  aBox.  aCinema.  aDavid Lynch.  aEpistemology.  aFilm History.  aGeorges Méliès.  aMedia Studies.  aMotiv.  aNarratology.  aSpace.  aStaging.2 aSwiss National Science Foundation (SNSF)efunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2z978311069629508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology, Education, Psychology 2020z9783110704549oZDB-23-SEW40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839448953zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de GruyterzOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839448953zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839448953/original  a978-3-11-069629-5 DG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2b2020  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2020  aZDB-23-GOA  aZDB-23-SEWb2020